          { "feature": "positive_trendelenburg_test", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Endovenous laser ablation (EVLA) or radiofrequency ablation (RFA). Foam sclerotherapy for branches. High ligation and stripping if not suitable for endovenous. Compression stockings post-op."
      },
      {
        "id": "reticular_and_telangiectasia",
        "name": "Reticular Veins and Telangiectasias (Spider Veins)",
