          { "feature": "bleeding_varicosity", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "superficial_thrombophlebitis", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Compression therapy (multi-layer bandaging). Wound care for ulcers. Endovenous ablation of incompetent truncal veins. Leg elevation. Superficial thrombophlebitis: NSAIDs, compression, anticoagulation if extensive."
      }
    ],

